{"title":"Rust desktop application","uid":"cb74cf4ec6063240bdd2492df0bbdf14","slug":"Rust-desktop-application","date":"2024-04-26T15:07:08.000Z","updated":"2024-05-03T09:00:37.603Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Rust-desktop-application.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/Rust-desktop-application-cover.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"Rust-Desktop-Application-Development-Practice\"><a href=\"#Rust-Desktop-Application-Development-Practice\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Rust Desktop Application Development Practice\"></a>Rust Desktop Application Development Practice</h1><p>在这一篇中准备记录一下本此次项目从选择到构筑实现的各种心路历程。而具体遇到的问题和注意应该会单独开一篇来记录。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"origin\"><a href=\"#origin\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"origin\"></a>origin</h2><p>这两天看到了这个视频📺，关于使用tauri+后端Rust🦀+数据库SurrealDB实现的一个桌面应用。</p>\n<p>恰好最近正在学习rsut🦀和数据库的相关知识，所以想要制作一个类似的✨桌面应用。前端使用什么还没有确定下来🤔。后端和数据库准备使用Rust🦀和SurrealDB。接下来准备开这个坑😎😎</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p>✨<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Lu4y1L78y?vd_source=f9e06439dfc1c172755ab9bcd65dbc97\">[使用Rust、Tauri和SurrealDB构建令人惊叹的桌面应用程序]中字</a></p>\n</div>\n<p>date: 2024-04-26</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"build-a-tauri-app\"><a href=\"#build-a-tauri-app\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"build a tauri app\"></a>build a tauri app</h2><p>✨经过讨论，我们最终决定使用tauri来作为我们的工具进行我们的app构筑😎</p>\n<p>✨也许我们的前端选择非常愚蠢。但是我们希望我们的前端ui能够实现我们的一些异想天开🧠</p>\n<p>✨最终选择最为基础的使用HTML、CSS、JavaScript来作为我们的前端语言实现🤔 </p>\n<h2 id=\"project-introduce\"><a href=\"#project-introduce\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"project introduce\"></a>project introduce</h2><ul>\n<li>项目名：Lumijade</li>\n<li>本次项目将由我们组织**<a href=\"https://github.com/VernunftIstWirklich\">VernunftIstWirklich</a>** 中的三个人共同开发💕</li>\n</ul>\n<p>—- 待续 —-</p>\n<p>date: 2024-04-27</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"rust+SurrealDB 一次灵感的产生，一次实践的开始","permalink":"/post/Rust-desktop-application","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":583,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Rust","slug":"Rust","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Rust.json"},{"name":"tauri","slug":"Rust/tauri","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Rust/tauri.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"rust","slug":"rust","count":3,"path":"api/tags/rust.json"},{"name":"SurrealDB","slug":"SurrealDB","count":1,"path":"api/tags/SurrealDB.json"},{"name":"tauri","slug":"tauri","count":2,"path":"api/tags/tauri.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Rust-Desktop-Application-Development-Practice\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Rust Desktop Application Development Practice</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#origin\"><span class=\"toc-text\">origin</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc